# 🌦️ Weather Checker

This is a simple web page built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** that shows the current weather for any city you enter.
You can also check your current location's weather in real time.

## 📌 Features

- ✅ Get weather by city name
- ✅ Detect your current location
- ✅ Show temperature in Celsius
- ✅ Display humidity
- ✅ Show a weather icon based on condition
- ✅ Change background image based on weather
- ✅ Error message for invalid city input

## 🧪 Technologies Used

- HTML  
- CSS 
- JavaScript 
- OpenWeatherMap API  https://home.openweathermap.org/api_keys

## 🔧 How to Run

1. Clone this repository or download the ZIP  
2. Open `index.html` in your browser  
3. Type a city name and click **"Get Weather"**  
4. Or click **"Use My Location"** to get current weather

## 🌐 Live Demo

👉 [Click here to view the app](https://weatherchecker-iqraproject.netlify.app/)


